summary: This is an email chain from July 6, 2019, with the subject 'Test' and containing two attachments related to Epstein operations: 'Epstein_Ops_Order.pdf' and 'Epstein_Attachment.pdf'. The email appears to be a test transmission of documents concerning Epstein.

events.title: Email transmission of Epstein documents
events.description: An email was sent with the subject 'Test' containing two attachments: 'Epstein_Ops_Order.pdf' and 'Epstein_Attachment.pdf'.

keyFacts: An email dated July 6, 2019, transmitted documents related to Epstein operations.
The email attachments were named 'Epstein_Ops_Order.pdf' and 'Epstein_Attachment.pdf'.
The email subject was 'Test', suggesting it may have been a trial transmission of sensitive documents.
